Generates a dbt staging model following best practices.
Staging models are 1:1 with source tables, with minimal transformations.

Template Variables:
- model_name: str - Model name (required, should start with stg_)
- source_name: str - Source name (required)
- source_table: str - Source table name (required)
- columns: List[ColumnDef] - Column definitions with renaming/casting
- description: str - Model description
- primary_key: str - Primary key column
- tenant_column: str - Tenant ID column (default: tenant_id)

